Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:03.32,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}找不到合适的话语　轻抚你的肩头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:09.95,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你一言不发　冷冷挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:16.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}小小的误解　令年轻的爱瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:23.59,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不想见你悲伤的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:30.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}即便抛弃梦想　请别抛弃你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:36.60,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}让它永远在我心中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}有一天　不同的你我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:44.71,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}携手筑起未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:51.47,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}回到曾经的地方　不论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:58.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}现在二人只有悲伤地错开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:03.51,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}相信后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:42.89,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}树荫下掩面而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:52.03,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}眼前是个陌生的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:19:01.71,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}奏起逝者之歌　古吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:10.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}星星陨落叹息　不归人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:19.72,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}莫要走　任凭如何呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:30.23,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}只留道边橘花静静摇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:38.41,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}稚嫩额头　残留的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:44.35,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}掌心温存　已渐渐散去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:57.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1500)}{\be1\an9}只留指尖拨颂的离别曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:15.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}依偎温柔臂膀的孩童心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:23.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}车轮无情甩开　呼啸前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:32.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}弹奏逝人叹息的古吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:40.27,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}激情触动心弦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:49.43,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}啊　悲伤染不尽的洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:59.13,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}绘出橘花摇摆夏日之影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:06.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}当额头不再稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:15.38,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}穿越赤土黄砂再远行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:24.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1500)}{\be1\an9}寻着离别的旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:38.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}焚尽回忆在大地飞驰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:47.05,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}是否懵生似曾相识之感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:29.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}目送拂晓之车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:39.18,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}彼时道边橘花　如今也一定在某处盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:47.44,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}如同那安宁的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:52.40,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}为再次找回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:59.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}不要熄灭灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:09.32,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1500)}{\be1}车轮　转动着…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布再三发来会谈邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 少来少来 已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多兵力没能拿下的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如让它趁早消失 以除后患
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边的准备马上完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题主要是贵方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两架
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要他们命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:16.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}飞向拂晓的宇宙
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.25,0:02:16.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}飞向拂晓的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达发现机影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士和战斗机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正向自凝岛上空靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士 抓紧出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的谈判要求置若罔闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌兹米大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 这就是回答吗 地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦视为敌人 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全部付诸武力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况 奥布没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没有胜算就放弃抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆来顺受 也很难做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是 为什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没人喜欢战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些东西必须靠行动守护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰相信为之而战的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是获得的勋章吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是父亲的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴能和你说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是命令你夺回那机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我们扎夫特也许不该介入这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看他们死！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得…准确地说 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次意见相同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲哪儿去了 昨天那两架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦瑞一尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨嗨 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天老老实实受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 你怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 红的也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些东西必须靠行动来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们颜色看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳尔德 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左转舵30
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次应该可以搞定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 我也出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人待在这种地方算什么事！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官的任务就是待在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点成熟起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌兹米大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作大约需要2小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别耽搁太久 已经只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令残存部队在迦具夜集结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃自凝岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布也真能坚持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种物量差距下只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明提防那个国家是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以地球军也急于求成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那批新机动战士的数据收集得如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经最优先进行采集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这个位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后可能与它们在战场相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉议长知道一定会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况有变化通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看来很无趣啊 伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想参加战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布拒绝了扎夫特的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多想了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待尘埃落定我们就返航卡本塔里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拿马一路航行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这狭窄的舰内想必很是郁闷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏就该有俘虏的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争不只是开枪对射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找一把钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后不经意间捡到了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 阿斯哈代表命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号立即撤离战线 降落迦具夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布的质量加速器设施！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 这没用的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就疲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你乱开枪 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去就自己飞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你傻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁允许你上来了 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦 快回去补给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样也打不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些废物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么强化了 还拿不出成果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧补给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 同志还需努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离奥布？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是说 要我们离开这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是职业军人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布被攻陷只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲大人 你怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民已经疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且有后勤保障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后世的骂名 由我们承担
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 失去奥布不能失去信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军幕后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蓝色宇宙盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩尔达·阿兹拉尔的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如今PLANT 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被掌控在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主张调整人种族论的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕德里克·萨拉手中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样发展下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将会陷入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两股互不相让的势力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无止境的争斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们甘愿接受 那样的未来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了另一个未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们保护火种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先一步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又会是一次艰难的远行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但相信你们明白它的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火种虽小但不会熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧安装推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道闭合 确认连接弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投射质量有变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会去宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机迅速登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迦具夜集结兵力？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他们算是背水一战了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯哈这老头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还垂死挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他们的狼狈样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要胜就胜得彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是草雉号的备用推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样动力十足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩格林齐射同时点火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引发不规则正电子反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮助进一步加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 回卡本塔里亚是个选择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但反正是跟地球军打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号方面怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 大家一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不可以留下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在对推进器进行最终检查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要他们抓紧 时间不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特的阿斯兰·萨拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从国家 服从军队讨伐敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是理所当然的 是无可厚非的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望 这样的战争早一天结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该和什么打 怎么打？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去找答案就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 这次别再浪费我的耐心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也开始有点想念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆地上进餐的滋味了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具夜周边气象数据全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达上有机影 是机动战士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯阁下 请尽快出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉号呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上起飞 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是空战 暴风不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥去大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首上仰20 罗恩格林待命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在这里磨蹭到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士接近 距离15
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有继承意志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就将完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌兹米大人 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 城坂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个傻女儿就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这副表情 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是奥布之狮的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲和你分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你并非孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你的父亲 我非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 城坂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认C管制以外人员全部撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有自动系统启动  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉号进入升空程序
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈乌梅亚之神与我们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:19:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种子飞走了 这便好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布和世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不会听从他们的摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那里的色彩已经不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历离别 伤痛 泪水 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前的 是光明吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是更大的战争漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的手 拼命想阻止黑暗降临？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「动荡的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开辟新的天际吧 高达

